{"tid":1196940,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有無主機可以2player連線上網打？","createTime":"2019-06-10T00:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T15:53:54.000Z","uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"46b9628489e7ca5fcf46890d7628a32939a34bea","tid":1196940,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:45:33.000Z","msg":"最近電腦壞咗，平時同老婆一人一部連機打，而家得返一部<br />\n為咗打機洗幾千買部電腦又好唔抵（我地只打TF2） <br />\n但唔買又只可以我打/佢打，另一個人就得個睇字<br />\n<br />\n成世仔未擁有過主機，想問下各位巴絲，PS, Xbox之類主機可唔可以做到我地一人一手制連線同街外打？細個去人屋企打PS3，我記得可以斬開個mon 2 player打。而家嗰啲得唔得？之前睇商場event有打World War Z，好似唔錯，有無得我左佢右，連出街同人打？<br />\n<br />\n如果有，有無咩game介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891f096485c658cc9f369ae110726206116d6e64","tid":1196940,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:10:42.000Z","msg":"無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb96fe0096186429e2b81c7e6cf844ea31dc81be","tid":1196940,"uid":37697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:27:09.000Z","msg":"而家啲主機咁廢仲想分mon打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10 fps都唔知得唔得"},{"pid":"1b3be8d8daf3a2d28759c5093b2190bfee2edc79","tid":1196940,"uid":255979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:28:22.000Z","msg":"認真答，冇"},{"pid":"42a817d5b53b17604d7e0dc18666daeab8ae6ada","tid":1196940,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb96fe0096186429e2b81c7e6cf844ea31dc81be","tid":1196940,"uid":37697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:27:09.000Z","msg":"而家啲主機咁廢仲想分mon打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10 fps都唔知得唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:37:22.000Z","msg":"即係以前啲無雙呀，高達呀兩個人打同一隻mon已成歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e47e65203fb0bcba9ee75df6edb1618e620f89","tid":1196940,"uid":37697,"like":1,"dislike"